    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1890-07-25T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1890-07-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="32"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d32">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Wharton</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Mizner</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1890-07-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 25, 1890</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Wharton advises Mr. Mizner that the Department has sent him five telegraphic
                    instructions, one of which was sent to Mr. Ryan to be repeated to him at
                    Guatemala.</p>
            </div>
